# AeroCraft Portal Structure

```
src/
  components/
    ComponentName/
      ComponentName.tsx   — one component
      index.ts            — barrel
  constants/
    numbers.const.ts      — TOPBAR_HEIGHT_PX, MAX_CONTENT_WIDTH_PX, etc.
    routes.const.ts       — ROUTES, URLs, AEROCRAFT_VERSION
    theme.const.ts        — BEAR_THEME, AC_PRIMARY, etc.
    index.ts
  i18n/
    types.ts              — Messages interface, Locale type
    en.ts                 — English messages
    es.ts                 — Spanish messages
    index.ts              — useI18n, useI18nState, I18nContext
  pages/
    PageName/
      PageName.tsx        — one page component
      index.ts
  shims/
    vue-stub.ts           — stub for Bear's Vue peer dep
  styles/
    aerocraft.css         — @aerocraft entry
    portal-surfaces.css   — portal + Bear theme layers
  App.tsx                 — BearProvider + Router + AppBar + Sidebar
  main.tsx                — createRoot
```

## Routing
- All routes defined as constants in `ROUTES` object in `routes.const.ts`
- Use `Route`, `Router`, `Link`, `useLocation` from `@forgedevstack/forge-compass`

## i18n
- All user-facing text keyed in `Messages` interface
- Never write UI strings directly in components — always `t.key`
- Locale stored in `localStorage` key `ac-locale`
